  "text": "Chemical analysis. Fermentation samples were filtered immediately through a 0.45-m membrane. The specific gravity was measured using a pycnometer. Until analysis was performed, the samples were frozen (Ϫ20°C) in 2-ml vial replicates. Malic and lactic acids were analyzed by high-performance liquid chromatography (Alliance 2690; Waters) with a photodiode array detector (Waters 996), as described previously [CITATION_1] .",
